suncertify.services
Class Contractor

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.services.Contractor
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Contractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Property-based representation of a database record, and also used for search criteria on the object level, as opposed to the string array-based record representation.

Unlike with the string array-based record representation, the order of the fields is not an issue here, regardless of what is specified in the metadata section of the database file. As a client does not have access to the database file, the Contractor object is the means to exchange information with the server, or between model and view.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Lars Kuettner
